      <title>新兴市场货币涨幅缩减，因交易员减少对美联储大幅降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/emerging-currencies-gain-stocks-extend-drop-before-us-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国通胀数据快于预期，导致交易员重新调整对美联储下周降息规模的押注，新兴市场股市连续第四个交易日下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/emerging-currencies-gain-stocks-extend-drop-before-us-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 10:53:56 GMT</pubDate>
